AUSTRALIAN OPEN
February 8, 2021
Pedro Martinez
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 
  P. MARTINEZ/Y. Nishioka
 6-7, 6-1, 6-1, 6-1
 THE MODERATOR:   Questions, please.
 Q. Can you walk us through your match and how you were feeling on court?
 PEDRO MARTINEZ:   The match was really tough at the beginning.  I started playing well, leading the set 5-1 in the first and I think I stopped believing in my serve in the game of the 5-1 to 5-2.  After I felt a little bit nervous, so came up, started to play good there and my level went down a little bit.
 But after that to lose a set like this, it's tough to accept, so I'm happy about to I can reach a really good level and keep it for four straight sets, and I'm really happy about that.
   
  
  
  
  

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT